{"tid":685203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[吉利好柒]特朗普據報禁德國豪華車進入美國市場","createTime":"2018-05-31T08:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T09:47:58.000Z","uid":31907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d454cda993c284fa2949360e21ab24dde8382eb","tid":685203,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:37:58.000Z","msg":"特朗普據報禁德國豪華車進入美國市場<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n德國經濟周刊(WirtschaftsWoche)報道，美國總統特朗普上月對法國總統馬克龍表示，將禁止德國豪華車廠商進入美國市場。<br />\n<br />\n該周刊引述多位歐洲和美國外交人員稱，特朗普將堅持其貿易政策，目的是讓平治汽車無法出現在紐約第五大道上。"},{"pid":"82351a30203e1cc25415c097f81e3aff04c61b20","tid":685203,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wQ1j-2_Hof8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwQ1j-2_Hof8&d=nmvs43czZi76FBiUJ2hPmTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=76fe8178\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wQ1j-2_Hof8</a>"}]}